Created 1.4.1955 out of the parishes of Easthampstad, Winkfield, 
    Warfield and Binfield. See also Table 2, note (d).

Abolished 1894 and divided into the parishes of Clewer Without 
    and Clewer Within.

Created 1894 from the part of the parish of Clewer in New Windsor 
    Municipal Borough. Abolished 1.4.1974 and added to the Windsor & 
    Maidenhead unparished area. See also Table 2, note (e).

Created 1894 from the rural part of the parish of Clewer. Abolished 
    1.4.1974 and added to the Windsor & Maidenhead unparished area. See also Table 2, 
    note (e).

Created 16.4.1880 by renaming  the parish of New Windsor with 
    Dedworth. Abolished 1.4.1974 and added to the Windsor & Maidenhead 
    unparished area. 
    See also Table 2, note (e).
Renamed 16.4.1880 to become the parish of New Windsor.

Created 25.3.1894 out of the parish of Old Windsor. See also Table 
    2, note (d).

Abolished 1.4.1974 and added to the Windsor & 
    Maidenhead unparished area. 
    See also Table 2, note (e).
